@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 01. A2A Supervisor Agent System Context (Python runtime)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

rectangle "Client Channel" {
  [Web UI / API Client] as Client
}

rectangle "Supervisor Agent (smart-supervisor)" {
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as supervisor_a2a_endpoint
  [supervisor_a2a_request_validator] as supervisor_a2a_request_validator
  [supervisor_agent_service] as supervisor_agent_service
  [supervisor_request_idempotency_service] as supervisor_request_idempotency_service
  [hitl_decision_service] as hitl_decision_service
  [supervisor_execution_persistence_service] as supervisor_execution_persistence_service #F3F4F6
  [supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory] as supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory
  [execution_consistency_coordinator] as execution_consistency_coordinator
  [supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service\n(lifecycle policy / read model)] as supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service #FFF4DB
  [supervisor_agent_orchestrator] as supervisor_agent_orchestrator #F3F4F6
  [LangGraph CompiledGraph] as langgraph_compiled_graph #DCEBFF
  [supervisor_planning_service] as supervisor_planning_service
  [a2a_invocation_service] as a2a_invocation_service
  [handoff_policy_service] as handoff_policy_service
  [supervisor_swarm_coordinator] as supervisor_swarm_coordinator
  [supervisor_response_compose_service] as supervisor_response_compose_service #FDE7C7
  [supervisor_a2ui_service] as supervisor_a2ui_service
  [default_supervisor_llm_runtime] as default_supervisor_llm_runtime
  [a2a_client_registry] as a2a_client_registry
  [supervisor_exception_handler] as supervisor_exception_handler
}

database "Stores / Redis or InMemory" as Stores {
  [Conversation Store] as ConversationStore #D9F7E8
  [Graph Checkpoint Store] as CheckpointStore #FFD9E2
  [Swarm State Store] as SwarmStateStore #E7D9FF
  [Review Store] as ReviewStore
  [Task Store] as TaskStore
  [Execution Snapshot Store] as ExecutionSnapshotStore
}

cloud "Downstream A2A Agents" {
  [Domain Agent A2A 1] as ProductAgent
  [Domain Agent A2A 2] as ReservationAgent
}

artifact "settings/app.yml / settings/supervisor.yml / settings/supervisor-hitl.yml" as Config

User --> Client
Client --> supervisor_a2a_endpoint : /a2a/supervisor\nJSON-RPC + SSE
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_a2a_request_validator
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_agent_service
supervisor_a2a_endpoint --> supervisor_exception_handler
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_request_idempotency_service
supervisor_agent_service --> hitl_decision_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_agent_orchestrator
supervisor_agent_service --> supervisor_planning_service
hitl_decision_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
supervisor_execution_persistence_service --> supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory
supervisor_persistence_strategy_factory --> execution_consistency_coordinator
supervisor_agent_orchestrator -[#4C8BF5]-> langgraph_compiled_graph
langgraph_compiled_graph --> a2a_invocation_service
langgraph_compiled_graph --> handoff_policy_service
langgraph_compiled_graph --> supervisor_swarm_coordinator
supervisor_agent_orchestrator -[#E3A23B]-> supervisor_response_compose_service
supervisor_response_compose_service --> supervisor_a2ui_service
supervisor_planning_service --> default_supervisor_llm_runtime
supervisor_response_compose_service --> default_supervisor_llm_runtime
a2a_invocation_service --> a2a_client_registry
a2a_client_registry --> Config
a2a_invocation_service --> ProductAgent
a2a_invocation_service --> ReservationAgent
supervisor_agent_orchestrator --> supervisor_execution_persistence_service
execution_consistency_coordinator --> TaskStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> ReviewStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> CheckpointStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> SwarmStateStore
execution_consistency_coordinator --> ExecutionSnapshotStore

note right of supervisor_agent_service
Current request entry flow
- validate + sanitize input
- planner-backed `review_required` evaluation
- planner review parse/runtime failure defaults to review-required or reject
- create immutable reviewed execution snapshot before WAITING_REVIEW
- create task state via lifecycle service
- execute orchestrator only when review is not required
- all Redis writes enter via persistence facade
- lifecycle service does not write Redis directly
- review APPROVE/CANCEL handled via tasks/review/* with snapshot token/version verification
end note

note right of supervisor_a2a_lifecycle_service
Lifecycle boundary
- task lifecycle policy and read model composition
- no direct Redis write
- persistence intent is delegated to facade
- system context collapses persistence path behind facade for readability
end note

note right of supervisor_agent_orchestrator
Current execution flow
- load immutable execution snapshot + history/checkpoint/swarm
- run LangGraph
- invoke downstream A2A agents
- evaluate/apply handoff
- compose text or A2UI response
- emit typed output events
- persist only final result channels to task state
end note
@enduml
